T02TD3095E:189a-0: snod gtsang zhing mdzes pa yid du 'ong @189a * //
T02TD3095E:189a-7: sman dang ldan par bya ste /
T02TD3095E:189a-8: de nas bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor pas aa k'a ros sbyangs te /
T02TD3095E:189a-9: nam mkha' mdzod kyis spel la /
T02TD3095E:189a-10: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsams te /
T02TD3095E:189a-11: de'i phyogs rnams su hr'i: las padma'i tshogs bskyed pa la phyogs skyong ba bcu la sogs pa chos kyi srung ma dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-12: khyad par du tshangs pa dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-13: dbang po dang legs ldan la sogs 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs bar bya'o //
T02TD3095E:189a-14: yang 'byung po'i gtor ma gnyis pa la lha'i gdon la sogs pa dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-15: zas su mdangs za bkun la sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD3095E:189a-16: de yang lce rdo rjer bsam zhing /
T02TD3095E:189a-17: spu gus bdud rtsi thams cad ngoms shing tshim par bya ba dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-18: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga char bzhin du 'byung bar bsam mo //
T02TD3095E:189a-19: de nas tha mar bzod par gsol te /
T02TD3095E:189a-20: gsol ba btab nas yi ge brgya pa brjod do //
T02TD3095E:189a-22: de yang 'byung po'i gtor ma ni mngal dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-28: btsas pa za ba la sogs pa la sbyin no //
T02TD3095E:189a-30: 'byung po gang dag ri rab steng gnas dang /
T02TD3095E:189a-32: bya ba nas zas su mngal za ba kun gyis sbyin no //
T02TD3095E:189a-33: gtor ma'i cho ga rdzogs so /
T02TD3095E:189a-35: // / pandi ta ma h'a dza na nyid kyi rang 'gyur yin gsung//
